    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "WESTERN SELECTION\nTasteful sampling\nSmoked salmon with cabbage wakame slaw\nand garden fresh salad with dressing of the day\nSavannah chicken breast with curry sauce and rice\nUnited Airlines is pleased to feature this entree,\ndesigned by America's own chef, Sheila Lukins.\nChampagne cake with toasted coconut\nREGIONAL SELECTION\nSelections are Chef Martin Yan specialties\nTasteful sampling\nSushi rolls and somen noodle salad with soba sauce\nSliced beef with shiitake mushrooms\nFresh seasonal fruit\nPRIOR TO ARRIVAL\nEnjoy our continental breakfast.\nWINES\nOffered with our compliments, J.P. Leconte Chardonnay\nand Rothschild Cadet Cabernet Sauvignon\nOTHER BEVERAGES\nSTARBUCKS. coffee, decaffeinated coffee, tea and\nselected soft drinks are available throughout the flight.\nWe apologize if occasionally your choice is not available.\n####\nCHAOME\n71%\nNRT-LAX/SFO (LD92-C96)\nECONOMY\n361Y002-3\n9/98\n2001,080.186",
      "UNITED\nmen u"
    ],
